title: Still Here
lyrics:
I can't make sense of the mess around me
I never knew You could feel so far away
Tragedy has shaken me and
I'm trembling on my knees again
When my world is torn apart

You remind me where You are



You are still here, You are still here

Drawing desperately near

Overwhelming my fear

You are still here



Your grace is strong when I'm at my weakest

You sing a song when I have no words to say

Your gravity is pulling me

From my tears up to my feet to rise again



You are still here, You are still here

Drawing desperately near

Overwhelming my fear

You are still here



Where can I go, what can I go through

Where Your love has never been and Your mercy doesn't win

You're my hope and You're my rescue

You are with me to the end, You're with me to the end



You are still here, You are still here

Drawing desperately near

Overwhelming my fear

You are still here
